\"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ByLayli Foroudi\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 15}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 46, \"to\": 52}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 90}, {\"ngram\": \"Photo\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 96}, {\"ngram\": \"FRANCOIS-XAVIER MARIT/AFP\", \"from\": 97, \"to\": 122}, {\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 174}, {\"ngram\": \"a traffic stop\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 217}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympics opening ceremony\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 298}, {\"ngram\": \"the distress\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 315}, {\"ngram\": \"the deceased teenager's family\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Romain Devassine, 26, shot 19-year-old Soheil El Khalfaoui as he tried to drive off during a traffic stop in Marseille on 4 August 2021.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 463, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9999999990400283, \"rank\": 9.598456471726086e-10, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Romain Devassine\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"19-year-old Soheil El Khalfaoui\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 412}, {\"ngram\": \"a traffic stop\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"4 August\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the past three years, the youngster's family have been pressing for justice and a murder investigation by Marseille justice authorities is ongoing.\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 602, \"end\": 611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9999999990400283, \"rank\": 9.598456471726086e-10, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past three years\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 516}, {\"ngram\": \"the youngster's family\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 540}, {\"ngram\": \"justice\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"a murder investigation\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So when Soheil's aunt, Samia El Khalfaoui, saw Devassine on television as she watched the opening ceremony, the shock it delivered felt akin to \\\"a cold shower\\\".\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Busia_District\", \"score\": 0.9870292156613839, \"rank\": 0.01314122964896173, \"text\": \"Samia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Busia_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Busia_District\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Soheil's aunt\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"Devassine\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"television\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"the shock\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"a cold shower\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more: \\\"I found it indecent, disrespectful.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was there, majestic on the stage in his Napoleon costume - it was as if he was mocking us,\\\" she told Reuters.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napoleon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.165195510221954e-27, \"text\": \"Napoleon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napoleon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Napoleon\"}, {\"begin\": 960, \"end\": 967,