ce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"their firearms\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"a refusal\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"a traffic stop\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"the driver\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"a risk\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"their life\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"physical safety\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ceremony spanned the centre of Paris, with performers dancing on rooftops, bridges and boats.Photo:DAN MULLAN Devassine published photos of the ceremony on his Instagram profile on 27 July.\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2047, \"end\": 2052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6842176798102979e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2115, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Divers_Alert_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0910978042663971e-15, \"text\": \"DAN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Divers_Alert_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Divers_Alert_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 2177, \"end\": 2186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7581912964782003e-23, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ceremony\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2024}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"performers\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\