rs were hired by a production agency.\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2542, \"end\": 2552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.0060858095221883e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all performers\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2583}, {\"ngram\": \"a production agency\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The most difficult thing is to think that three years have passed and he is doing his stunts on TV while the investigative judge still has not interrogated him - if the judge had done his work, he would not be on TV,\\\" said Issam El Khalfaoui, Soheil's father.\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The most difficult thing\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2645}, {\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"his stunts\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"the investigative judge\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"the judge\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"his work\", \"from\": 2805, \"to\": 2813}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"Issam El Khalfaoui\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"Soheil's father\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Marseille prosecutor's office declined to comment.\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2886, \"end\": 2895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9999999990400283, \"rank\": 9.598456471726086e-10, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}], \"noun_phr